# Class: obo:FLUXO_0000022 (steady state flux solution space)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:FLUXO_0000022 "An information content entity that contains set of all possible flux vectors that are consistent with reaction stoichiometries and a set of flux constraints at metabolic steady state.")
AnnotationAssertion(oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym obo:FLUXO_0000022 "flux polytope")
