AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:FLUXO_0000033 "The information content entity that describes the rate of change of an intracellular metabolite concentration is considered negligible, which holds when the metabolic flux through the metabolite pools is much larger than the change in their pool sizes over time.")
