AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:FLUXO_0000196 "A data transformation which aims to take into account the contribution of natural random variation in isotopic composition in the environment and adjust for it during the calculation of mass isotopologue distribution in a tracer based metabolomics experiment.")
AnnotationAssertion(oboInOwl:hasDbXref obo:FLUXO_0000196 "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/MSIO_0000130")
