AnnotationAssertion(oboInOwl:hasDbXref obo:FLUXO_0000197 "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000704")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment obo:FLUXO_0000197 "It describes the strength or intensity of a solution in terms of its solute content. It is therefore a ratio in which the numerator is a measure of the solute and the denominator is a measure of the solvent.")
