AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:FLUXO_0000210 "A data item that is required to run a fluxomics investigation."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000116 obo:FLUXO_0000210 "Sergi: I'm not sure that this is a subclass of information about software. These do not refer to the software itself, but are instead things we use to calculate something using the software. Maybe move to specifically dependent continuant?")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label obo:FLUXO_0000210 "fluxomics parameter")
