AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment obo:FLUXO_0000241 "Several commonly used metabolic flux units are per volume: nmol ⋅ hr⁻¹ ⋅ μl⁻¹ of cells or mol ⋅ hr⁻¹ ⋅ cell⁻¹ and per biomass: mmol ⋅ gDW⁻¹ ⋅ hr⁻¹ (where gDW stands for grams of dry cell weight).")
