AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment obo:FLUXO_0000260 "If the number of observations made is large enough, the sampling distribution can be assumed to be normal, which entails that 95% of the sampling distributions falls within roughly2 (1.96) standard deviations from the mean.")
